      "=========================================\n",
      "Law 1: ~(A V B) = ~A ^ ~B\n",
      "=========================================\n",
      "LHS:  {'x1': 0.5, 'x3': 0.0, 'x2': 0.3}\n",
      "RHS:  {'x1': 0.5, 'x3': 0.0, 'x2': 0.3}\n",
      "-> Law 1 is PROVED!\n",
      "\n",
      "=========================================\n",
      "Law 2: ~(A ^ B) = ~A V ~B\n",
      "=========================================\n",
      "LHS:  {'x1': 0.7, 'x3': 0.2, 'x2': 0.6}\n",
      "RHS:  {'x1': 0.7, 'x3': 0.2, 'x2': 0.6}\n",
      "-> Law 2 is PROVED!\n"
     ]
